name: My name is great power
description: Remember the image, rotate the whirlpool, the color of the rune depends on what level it affects, your consciousness should color the rune itself. This rune should be presented where it is necessary to produce an effect. This rune directs the energy of life and its effect is felt precisely as power. It can power anything you want, but in the standard scenario, you will most likely be able to apply it only to your body. With the help of it, you can increase the capabilities of your body, for example, run more than you usually can, relieve fatigue... In some cases, it can even restore the work of failed organs and this is just the tip of the iceberg of its application!
